/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/#I_%E2%80%93_LOI_ICH_HOC_GIA_SU_DOI_VOI_HOC_SINH_TIEU_HOC\" >I &#8211; L\u1ee2I \u00cdCH H\u1eccC GIA S\u01af \u0110\u1ed0I V\u1edaI H\u1eccC SINH TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/#II_%E2%80%93_DOI_NGU_GIA_SU_GIOI_%E2%80%93_CO_NGHIEP_VU_SU_PHAM\" >II &#8211; \u0110\u1ed8I NG\u0168 GIA S\u01af GI\u1eceI &#8211; C\u00d3 NGHI\u1ec6P V\u1ee4 S\u01af PH\u1ea0M<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/#_Gia_su_la_giao_vien\" >? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/#_Gia_su_la_sinh_vien\" >? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/#III_%E2%80%93_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_DAY_KEM_TIEU_HOC\" >III &#8211; H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af D\u1ea0Y K\u00c8M TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/#IV_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_QUYEN_LOI_HOC_SINH\" >IV &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M &amp; QUY\u1ec0N L\u1ee2I H\u1eccC SINH<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-l