an style=\"color: #333399; font-size: 110%;\"><b>D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399; font-size: 110%;\"><b>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #333399; font-size: 110%;\"><b>\u00a0 Hotline: 0963.138.511 &#8211; 0862.856.500<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #282828;\"><strong>GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH MINH &#8211; CUNG C\u1ea4P GIA S\u01af T\u1ea4T C\u1ea2 C\u00c1C M\u00d4N<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\">\n<table id=\"tablepress-35\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-35\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<th class=\"column-1\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m c\u00e1c m\u00f4n v\u0103n h\u00f3a: To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, H\u00f3a, Anh, Ti\u1ec3u H\u1ecdc, Ng\u1eef V\u0103n, L\u1ecbch S\u1eed.... t\u1eeb L\u1edbp 1 \u0111\u1ebfn L\u1edbp 12, \u00d4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc.<\/th><th class=\"column-2\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m c\u00e1c m\u00f4n ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef: Ti\u1ebfng H\u00e0n, Ti\u1ebfng Trung, Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt....<\/th><th class=\"column-3\">Luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p, \u00f4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi... gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh thi \u0111\u1ed7 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 cao<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-35 from cache --><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">Trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cung c\u1ea5p cho qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 \u1edf c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0H\u00e0nh trang v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 1<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Ti\u1ebfng anh cho tr\u1ebb em<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0To\u00e1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng vi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh kh\u00f3a t\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1edbp 5<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Luy\u1ec7n ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p cho h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0R\u00e8n t\u01b0 duy n\u00e2ng cao<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0\u00d4n thi v\u00e0o l\u1edbp 6<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3822 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GIA-SU-TIEU-HOC.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GIA-SU-TIEU-HOC.png 1000w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GIA-SU-TIEU-HOC-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/GIA-SU-TIEU-HOC-768x461.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_LOI_ICH_HOC_GIA_SU_DOI_VOI_HOC_SINH_TIEU_HOC\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #d83131;\"><strong>I &#8211; L\u1ee2I \u00cdCH H\u1eccC GIA S\u01af \u0110\u1ed0I V\u1edaI H\u1eccC SINH TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y 1 k\u00e8m 1<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, t\u01b0 duy c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen t\u1ed1t trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc: T\u01b0 th\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i h\u1ecdc, t\u00e1c phong t\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc, k\u0129 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00e0i c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9&#8230;<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><strong style=\"color: #000000;\">Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ec3u H\u1ecdc<\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c em n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, y\u00eau th\u00edch m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc &amp; ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em>B\u00e1m s\u00e1t h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c, l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh cho ph\u1ee5 huynh m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em> Gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111i l\u1ea1i, giao th\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u00f3n.<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em>R\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n t\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1ef1 \u00fd th\u1ee9c nghi\u00eam ch\u1ec9nh h\u1ecdc h\u00e0nh.<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em>Ph\u1ee5 huynh n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh, y\u1ebfu trong h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho c\u00e1c em.<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_DOI_NGU_GIA_SU_GIOI_%E2%80%93_CO_NGHIEP_VU_SU_PHAM\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #e14d43;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">II &#8211; \u0110\u1ed8I NG\u0168 GIA S\u01af GI\u1eceI &#8211; C\u00d3 NGHI\u1ec6P V\u1ee4 S\u01af PH\u1ea0M<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 110%;\">Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn k\u0129 c\u00e0ng t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, kinh nghi\u1ec7m,\u2026. th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 gia s\u01b0 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff; font-size: 110%;\"><em>? Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, gia s\u01b0 c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <strong>\u0110I\u1ec2M Y\u1ebeU<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00e0i thi, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0:\u00a0<strong>T\u00cdNH C\u1ea8U TH\u1ea2<\/strong>, s\u1ef1 n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00e0i, c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y,\u2026. \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 gi\u1ecdng<strong> kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ecdng, ph\u00e1t \u00e2m r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, t\u00e2m l\u00fd<\/strong> v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 110%;\"><em><strong>? Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh g\u1ed3m 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169:<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Gia_su_la_giao_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 110%;\"><b>? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean:<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">+ L\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh quy khoa s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m ti\u1ebfng anh chuy\u00ean ngh\u00e0nh ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">+ Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u1edbp t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">+ Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1ef1 do chuy\u00ean \u0111i d\u1ea1y gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3810 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU.png 1000w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/DOI-NGU-GIA-SU-768x461.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Gia_su_la_sinh_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 110%;\"><b>? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean:<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">+ Gia s\u01b0 thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0110H s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4, \u0110H gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c &#8211; \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">+ Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng top \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u00ean d\u1ea1y ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0: \u0110H S\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110H KTQD, B\u00e1ch Khoa&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">+\u00a0C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t, phong th\u00e1i nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">+ T\u00e1c phong chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u1ecbch d\u1ea1y \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, gi\u1edd gi\u1ea5c\u00a0\u0111\u00fang h\u1eb9n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">+ Ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00ec v\u00e0 ph\u00e0n h\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 huynh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_DAY_KEM_TIEU_HOC\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #d83131;\"><strong>III &#8211; H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af D\u1ea0Y K\u00c8M TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3823 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-Tieu-hoc-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-Tieu-hoc-1.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-Tieu-hoc-1-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-Tieu-hoc-1-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tham kh\u1ea3o. H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 <span style=\"\">096.31.38.511<\/span> ho\u1eb7c <span style=\"\">0862.856.500<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">******************<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\">? Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc th\u1eed Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3812 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-300x201.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-768x515.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #0000ff;\">=&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333399;\">h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0<\/span><\/strong><\/a> t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1-12, \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu, ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0<\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-500-gia-su-mon-toan-gioi-tu-lop-1-12-o-ha-noi\/\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/span><\/a> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u2013 H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 120k &#8211; gi\u00e1 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i h\u01a1n h\u1ecdc trung t\u00e2m 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi &#8211; Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 g\u1ea5p 5 l\u1ea7n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/em><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng anh<\/strong><\/span><\/a> ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 &#8211; Con h\u1ecdc Ti\u1ebfng Anh chu\u1ea9n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_QUYEN_LOI_HOC_SINH\"><\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">IV &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M &amp; QUY\u1ec0N L\u1ee2I H\u1eccC SINH<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">Cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0<strong>\u00a0MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd \u2013 \u0110\u00daNG &amp; CHU\u1ea8N<\/strong>\u00a0theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 th\u00f4ng tin r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ee9ng minh th\u01b0 &amp; th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">T\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0<strong>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/strong>.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>Gia s\u01b0\u00a0<strong>NGHI\u00caM T\u00daC<\/strong>\u00a0trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>T\u1eadn t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u1ea1y h\u1ebft b\u00e0i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft gi\u1edd.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>D\u1ea1y \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecdc sinh &amp; gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 24\/7 tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong>? V\u1edbi 12 n\u0103m trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01a1n 15.000+ gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ebd <span style=\"font-size: 105%;\">gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong><em>=&gt;&gt;&gt; <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Xem th\u00eam<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-gia-su-luyen-chu-dep-tai-nha-tien-bo-chi-sau-1-thang\/\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n vi\u1ebft ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/span><\/a> \u2013 Luy\u1ec7n n\u00e9t ch\u1eef, r\u00e8n n\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.